	<article class="post-7513 post type-post status-publish hentry category-attention-counselors category-behind-the-admissions-door category-college-applications category-for-juniors category-for-parents category-for-seniors category-guidance-office tag-harvard-university tag-harvarddean tag-william-r-fitzsimmons" id="post-7513">
	<header class="postHeader">
